{
  "id": "654ad523feb812001c52c372",
  "title": "ダーウィンとメンデル",
  "created": 1699403046,
  "updated": 1699447746,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "654ad523feb812001c52c372",
      "text": "ダーウィンとメンデル",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403046,
      "updated": 1699403046
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad859ed60e60000019679",
      "text": "[FountainPen_LG.icon][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403867,
      "updated": 1699404728
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad524ed60e60000b7fec4",
      "text": " [メンデル]は[豆]を大量に栽培して[顕性遺伝と潜性遺伝の法則]を調べた",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699403046,
      "updated": 1699447740
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad572ed60e60000b7fec7",
      "text": "  実験に基づいた学説の提唱",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403124,
      "updated": 1699404818
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad588ed60e60000b7fec8",
      "text": "  順序を入れ替えても良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403146,
      "updated": 1699404818
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad5a5ed60e60000b7fec9",
      "text": "   仮説を立てて、実験をし、仮説を検証した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403175,
      "updated": 1699404818
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad5b6ed60e60000b7fecb",
      "text": " [ダーウィン]は[進化論]を唱えたが、(特に当時は) 証明するのが難しい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699403192,
      "updated": 1699447746
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad5eaed60e60000b7fecc",
      "text": "  今だと世代サイクルが短い個体とかで遺伝子を調べたりして実験できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403243,
      "updated": 1699404818
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad62eed60e60000b7fecd",
      "text": " より科学的だと言われるのはメンデルの方法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403311,
      "updated": 1699404818
    },
    {
      "id": "654adc1ded60e60000b7fed4",
      "text": " ダーウィン型の方法で仮説を立てて理論を作る人もいる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699404831,
      "updated": 1699404862
    },
    {
      "id": "654ad52aed60e60000b7fec5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1699403052,
      "updated": 1699403052
    }
  ]
}